Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average resolution time for Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Minimum time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time for Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to be followed by a re-submission by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time until a case with Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR is closed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average time to re-approve after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time for all activities following Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR until Payment Handled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average waiting time until Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR after Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to the next activity in the process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases with Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR leading to Payment Handled
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time it takes from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for cases to be resolved after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case
